Ella H. was struggling to pay $2,114/month for her apartment in Jacksonville, Florida, after her adult kids moved out, and she became an empty nester. She found PadSplit’s rooms for rent on Facebook and now saves $1,200/month, allowing her to save to buy a home!⁠
⁠
“PadSplit is a 10/10! I wouldn't change anything - I love where I live!" says Ella.
